==Notes==
<references group="note">
<ref name="Kazuhiko">[[Komatsu Kazuhiko]], in the book 「器物の妖怪 - 付喪神をめぐって」（『憑霊信仰論』 [[講談社]]〈[[講談社学術文庫]]〉、1994年、326-342頁。{{ISBN|4-06-159115-0}}） used the word "Tsukugami" widely to include any [[yōkai]], including animals, from the Edo period and before that originally came from tools.</ref>
</references>

